        "briefDescription": "Under the scheme, financial assistance in the form of maternity benefits shall be provided to women construction workers registered under the Board during their maternity period. ",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The “Maternity Benefit” is a social security scheme, implemented by the Meghalaya Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board (MBOCWWB), Labour Department, Government of Meghalaya. Under the scheme, financial assistance in the form of maternity benefits shall be provided to women construction workers registered under the Board during their maternity period.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n   1. The registered women construction workers shall receive financial assistance of ₹1,000/- as maternity benefits during their maternity period.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "",
